        {
            "title": "日圓勢創2024年以來最佳單周表現 財政擔憂暫時緩解",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 日圓勢將創下2024年11月以來的最大單周漲幅，市場樂觀預期日本首相高市早苗的勝選將使她能夠在維持金融市場信任的同時擴大財政刺激規模。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">日圓兌美元匯率已連續四個交易日走強，本周迄今上漲約2.8%。風險資產跌勢加深，避險需求也支撐了日圓匯率。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">投資者將高市的壓倒性勝利解讀為政治不確定性降低，財政出現最壞結果的風險減弱，從而提振了日圓，並推動日本國債殖利率從上月觸及的多年高位回落。在周一舉行的新聞發布會上，高市承認市場對食品銷售稅減稅兩年表示擔憂，並重申避免發行債券為該措施提供資金的計畫。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-0ed1e079-b93c-3bbd-9c97-2a27c0b128ce-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：無視美國強勁的就業數據 對沖基金調轉船頭看漲日圓</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「自民黨取得壓倒性勝利後，財政擔憂緩解，以及對日本央行加息的預期，導致日圓走強，」三井住友信託銀行的駐紐約交易員Takeru Yamamoto表示。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/6PtXmdcBXF039q5cBjgXng--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/no/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/b8f83f19617b9bf4db3bcde825c618a9\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">日本外匯事務最高官員三村淳表示，儘管日圓本周走強，但政府仍對匯率走勢保持高度警惕。圍繞政府可能出手支撐日圓的不安情緒，也限制了日圓下行。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">隔夜指數掉期顯示，日本央行4月加息的可能性約為78%。投資者將密切關注日本央行官員Naoki Tamura周五的講話以及美國CPI數據，以幫助判斷美日利差和日圓走勢。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Yen Set for Best Week Since 2024 as Fiscal Concerns Put on Hold</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">—聯合報導 Hidenori Yamanaka、Michael Ball.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%97%A5%E5%9C%93%E5%8B%A2%E5%89%B52024%E5%B9%B4%E4%BB%A5%E4%BE%86%E6%9C%80%E4%BD%B3%E5%96%AE%E5%91%A8%E8%A1%A8%E7%8F%BE-%E8%B2%A1%E6%94%BF%E6%93%94%E6%86%82%E6%9A%AB%E6%99%82%E7%B7%A9%E8%A7%A3-022031551.html",
